lead_paragraph: Having ended his career once in London on what he considered a sour note, Michael Phelps enters the Rio de Janeiro Olympics pool for his second swansong determined to bow out on his own terms.

headline.main: Phelps Hoping Rio Swansong Hits the Right Notes
